lockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑"},{"pid":"5d4485d853cbcf8b5139719ec98a3be9edafd21f","tid":47942,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21dd3d878da9537bb2878356349392f452658082","tid":47942,"uid":56210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:01:38.000Z","msg":"得你咁豁達咪好囉 !<br />\n我就唔得喇"},{"pid":"e79cdb04033b90fac44579bed02331c6edcab6d4","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生活艱難到一個地步可能會原諒<br />\n如果係為左貪心而做 我諗佢個格都唔方好得去邊<br />\nbtw 驗身先好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb59b4adfcff9244a8641fd8632d7948b62698c","tid":47942,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"砵蘭修女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5655b60128ae7568f5535eacfea40e1745892e4","tid":47942,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢做夜總會係做左幾耐？幾深入先？都有分扑同唔扑架好似<br />\n有冇問佢咩原因而做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n價值觀好有問題，<br />\n物質主義大過一切，<br />\n飛得#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"023ede7637f1d9685a010c9a08e2754355a26782","tid":47942,"uid":32396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生活艱難到一個地步可能會原諒<br />\n如果係為左貪心而做 我諗佢個格都唔方好得去邊<br />\nbtw 驗身先好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲"},{"pid":"f3b9e4f13171dadd63b11e67d1da7356f452bf7a","tid":47942,"uid":64911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"之前學校course 有個夜總會女仔黎講talk 會睇得出佢真係貪錢做 同埋做得多數有壞習慣，我覺得唔ok"},{"pid":"12b11350f1337cc3e82cca4d33aef7a9acbc70f8","tid":47942,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢做夜總會係做左幾耐？幾深入先？都有分扑同唔扑架好似<br />\n有冇問佢咩原因而做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢當初入行既原因係咁，咁唔再做既原因又係咩？<br />\n你覺得眼前既佢仲係咪個物質主義/貪錢既人？"},{"pid":"39b8c099db21a51b44d54ce93adaf729fe1d12f8","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前學校course 有個夜總會女仔黎講talk 會睇得出佢真係貪錢做 同埋做得多數有壞習慣，我覺得唔ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會有咩壞習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acc5f662d7506d1b82e1b6367dbee7bc1541ffa","tid":47942,"uid":22073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"金魚都接受到既"},{"pid":"625051ba10463ee102e8372ee836cb96009b94bb","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生活艱難到一個地步可能會原諒<br />\n如果係為左貪心而做 我諗佢個格都唔方好得去邊<br />\nbtw 驗身先好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2431b906a8cbd1b15b787075365fbbb31ef8450b","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金魚都接受到既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金魚會唔會都偷偷比啲唔識既叔叔扑？"},{"pid":"5ef4257c2fd289677f8fbd2b9fd140abd57462ce","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢做夜總會係做左幾耐？幾深入先？都有分扑同唔扑架好似<br />\n有冇問佢咩原因而做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢當初入行既原因係咁，咁唔再做既原因又係咩？<br />\n你覺得眼前既佢仲係咪個物質主義/貪錢既人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後先知一齊左之後先無做"},{"pid":"eeaf22846d7788d52eccb38e3894f0a4b5c1811c","tid":47942,"uid":68276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"如果係女友屋企開夜總會又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401d1c8d5179ddb2aca31fb0a33bbe7bba03079e","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係女友屋企開夜總會又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一定唔會做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e50fab2e2964715603ff717f82165949a3aa099","tid":47942,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生活艱難到一個地步可能會原諒<br />\n如果係為左貪心而做 我諗佢個格都唔方好得去邊<br />\nbtw 驗身先好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩，因為個d男人無諗住同佢過人世<br />\n佢哋既心態就係咁撚畸形<br />\n你呢條刺好難拔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951295554db89cba8ecf45f25cbf4c7e73f795d7","tid":47942,"uid":218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"為物慾去做嘅飛硬<br />\n隨時一路同你拍拖一路繼續做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc26b899ccd796a277bf28aa605e5cce731d994","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為物慾去做嘅飛硬<br />\n隨時一路同你拍拖一路繼續做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就應該無再做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b5a7138a3532c852e5a0a66a6dae849428a3e1","tid":47942,"uid":4083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前學校course 有個夜總會女仔黎講talk 會睇得出佢真係貪錢做 同埋做得多數有壞習慣，我覺得唔ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩學校咁型？"},{"pid":"2bb27ae79eab4d4396d7928ca7b24753a03c6bf9","tid":47942,"uid":11019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"會 感覺上同做雞冇分別"},{"pid":"d79994e135710e57110a3b40b096c248fecb5bda","tid":47942,"uid":25627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:24:11.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"d21196227121b9fc6a2cb67260a62d614ca84c24","tid":47942,"uid":32396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔關你事 係果d男人鳩痕姐<br />\n你女朋友應該幾靚女<br />\n同埋佢實話無問顯 因為佢唔想個問題落係佢身上 <br />\n一齊左先唔做 條刺更深 佢唔做 邊有錢買名牌<br />\n你要留意下佢依排有無新名牌 有既姐係仲有做"},{"pid":"b6356d243d3986809fec3a3c74eb8bd7ae802f66","tid":47942,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"你唔做雞我邊有錢養你呀"},{"pid":"375629597e928e4217409ca5b52673b16d01b14d","tid":47942,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為物慾去做嘅飛硬<br />\n隨時一路同你拍拖一路繼續做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就應該無再做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你未發現到啫 貪念大嘅人咁易回到頭咩<br />\n識人做過金魚 釣到金龜之後仲大條道理出軌<br />\n做得嗰行思想多數奇奇怪怪<br />\n千錯萬錯都唔會係佢錯<br />\n襯早斬纜啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142bdb69503a160890a85751703eef8d375290a1","tid":47942,"uid":42695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:29:15.000Z","msg":"係咪俏XX？呢間好多女做兼職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47709bc31533b9af241dc5dc5136dd2083dbbc9e","tid":47942,"uid":62115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e19d2a053758eb6c544a039f2fa004dbc7e29c","tid":47942,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>為物慾去做嘅飛硬<br />\n隨時一路同你拍拖一路繼續做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就應該無再做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你未發現到啫 貪念大嘅人咁易回到頭咩<br />\n識人做過金魚 釣到金龜之後仲大條道理出軌<br />\n做得嗰行思想多數奇奇怪怪<br />\n千錯萬錯都唔會係佢錯<br />\n襯早斬纜啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你為左錢可以向三唔識七既人賣自己身體既<br />\n俾有錢仔溝下仲唔腿張開咩"},{"pid":"f7dd8812b284fb44f5e0a867b96c9cb1bf2e5c39","tid":47942,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4783dab89c418f1cd414e6557865c1cf501d8f2","tid":47942,"uid":17945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"你女朋友都唔會介意你番過工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c970d4aee3e1adae3585a9b66094b92b2784388e","tid":47942,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"你女朋友姓吳？"},{"pid":"e763eb0b1a3dd2b6d7df7ff3bc742d0461febc2a","tid":47942,"uid":40028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢做夜總會係做左幾耐？幾深入先？都有分扑同唔扑架好似<br />\n有冇問佢咩原因而做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n介紹你女友黎識"},{"pid":"30feba75bfa25d4f2767fa90e39c511ecc00f561","tid":47942,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生活艱難到一個地步可能會原諒<br />\n如果係為左貪心而做 我諗佢個格都唔方好得去邊<br />\nbtw 驗身先好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢想你唔介意咪咁講囉 正路點會唔介意"},{"pid":"c1b23a9699e32433473bc0232a78b43f79a9d435","tid":47942,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"873e61f9ec59b931f09bac7853e772882d97c09c","tid":47942,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生活艱難到一個地步可能會原諒<br />\n如果係為左貪心而做 我諗佢個格都唔方好得去邊<br />\nbtw 驗身先好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢想你唔介意咪咁講囉 正路點會唔介意</blockquote><br />\n不如話佢自己根本唔覺得有問題<br />\n即係完全冇覺得後悔<br />\n既然以前用開名牌 而家可唔可以唔用名牌先<br />\n如果唔係的話 除左樓主係有錢佬<br />\n否則多多都唔夠佢洗啦<br />\n以前係點固然重要<br />\n而家係點先係最重要"},{"pid":"9fa1da87031d7702c707ebcbc5d0b2f303a452f9","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢想你唔介意咪咁講囉 正路點會唔介意</blockquote><br />\n不如話佢自己根本唔覺得有問題<br />\n即係完全冇覺得後悔<br />\n既然以前用開名牌 而家可唔可以唔用名牌先<br />\n如果唔係的話 除左樓主係有錢佬<br />\n否則多多都唔夠佢洗啦<br />\n以前係點固然重要<br />\n而家係點先係最重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係有錢佬 只係對佢好好啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84c44ece7c74ee9d783ae9d24cd7e9ae2e137d","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金魚?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係"},{"pid":"b5d1102db64b818d1666fbc1b2b8bff8b34bc6e2","tid":47942,"uid":68298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:20:19.000Z","msg":"你條女係雞 三萬蚊過夜<br />\n中出多幾劑就好飛左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b459f8f77e4838625085b2ba9fabc41602e3f607","tid":47942,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢想你唔介意咪咁講囉 正路點會唔介意</blockquote><br />\n不如話佢自己根本唔覺得有問題<br />\n即係完全冇覺得後悔<br />\n既然以前用開名牌 而家可唔可以唔用名牌先<br />\n如果唔係的話 除左樓主係有錢佬<br />\n否則多多都唔夠佢洗啦<br />\n以前係點固然重要<br />\n而家係點先係最重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係有錢佬 只係對佢好好啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢放唔放得低d名牌？"},{"pid":"61f45915b92ee743b6c9ef37d700be8a2ea0b151","tid":47942,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:29:22.000Z","msg":"追求物質上既享受同個人既價值觀正唔正確係兩回事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都係好鐘意買名牌果d人黎，但我從來無諗過做妓女/ptgf/夜總會etc<br />\n我所有名牌都係靠自己翻埋d得最低工資多少少人工既垃圾工儲錢買翻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學歷低無咩技能賺大錢唔可以當做籍口將呢件事合理化囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且名牌又唔係咩必須品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話係屋企有事需要用錢呀/交學費呀/已經翻左好多份工都唔夠錢用etc 都話令人容易接受d<br />\n同埋樓主會介意但條女覺得唔介意既，已經證明你地兩個價值觀唔太一致"},{"pid":"38fba58bcfc861c6af8a5234ad01b64e41517868","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T21:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n不如話佢自己根本唔覺得有問題<br />\n即係完全冇覺得後悔<br />\n既然以前用開名牌 而家可唔可以唔用名牌先<br />\n如果唔係的話 除左樓主係有錢佬<br />\n否則多多都唔夠佢洗啦<br />\n以前係點固然重要<br />\n而家係點先係最重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係有錢佬 只係對佢好好啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢放唔放得低d名牌？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會叫我搵錢買...."},{"pid":"02a9da35d2a6b1e74f39ec8934005e0109061b22","tid":47942,"uid":57418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/071928_a4f60a2e127b60b16e33c234aed960f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=