\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc</blockquote><br />\n價值觀有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e707f4c78b1d4af42883950993f9502b457ad32","tid":47942,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:48:46.000Z","msg":"依D女唔可以留得耐，飛啦"},{"pid":"1d0b309cc58855144a8fa5b421ede78191f85ec7","tid":47942,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>追求物質上既享受同個人既價值觀正唔正確係兩回事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都係好鐘意買名牌果d人黎，但我從來無諗過做妓女/ptgf/夜總會etc<br />\n我所有名牌都係靠自己翻埋d得最低工資多少少人工既垃圾工儲錢買翻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學歷低無咩技能賺大錢唔可以當做籍口將呢件事合理化囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且名牌又唔係咩必須品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話係屋企有事需要用錢呀/交學費呀/已經翻左好多份工都唔夠錢用etc 都話令人容易接受d<br />\n同埋樓主會介意但條女覺得唔介意既，已經證明你地兩個價值觀唔太一致</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一句都agger<br />\n但為左物慾而做雞價值觀就唔正常喇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18313b8e3f952233762c59886dc6c27956981d4d","tid":47942,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:50:37.000Z","msg":"價值觀唔一樣, 遲早都會散"},{"pid":"fe8a3dae3fbb9bb72bf37e252279527787439ffd","tid":47942,"uid":68208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢做夜總會係做左幾耐？幾深入先？都有分扑同唔扑架好似<br />\n有冇問佢咩原因而做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又知無扑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab84c4cdf486002650bdb57bfec4d8ac7f50f88c","tid":47942,"uid":1265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:56:33.000Z","msg":"算啦 條女都係想搵個傻仔要住先<br />\n再釣下金龜<br />\n釣唔到都有個傻仔肯埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75482c7dd526ef1e6da1e840a5c96f0e380240b","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢做夜總會係做左幾耐？幾深入先？都有分扑同唔扑架好似<br />\n有冇問佢咩原因而做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係為左名牌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔扑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又知無扑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講 佢話人地開幾多錢都唔會扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話啲朋友都係咁 我都唔知真定假"},{"pid":"46d31a00da3739337d9691fa78d12fcaf8089e1b","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T23:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦 條女都係想搵個傻仔要住先<br />\n再釣下金龜<br />\n釣唔到都有個傻仔肯埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 你講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2961a7ae68ea71583b700fe6528f80ae7467320","tid":47942,"uid":21111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:00:49.000Z","msg":"講咩都無用 你熱戀期都聽唔入架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我估你都係假膠黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222bb6cd6ccbe3a220e3dffcbb5f40a4c8744e3d","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咁佢放唔放得低d名牌？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會叫我搵錢買....</blockquote><br />\n即係咪又係雞，仲要話其他男人唔介意，你回頭就唔介意，但點睇佢都係無人要隻臭雞之後搵毒丁埋單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身邊有幾個朋友都同夜總會小姐結婚。。我都唔個係我太介意定點 結婚真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfe75c53eacefc164402b39e83dc72b33c76adb","tid":47942,"uid":44179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b664cc390af2d6ff0472ed9851db830cc8582b3","tid":47942,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:10:34.000Z","msg":"咖喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef5dfff8681d17a1c874b7821d2a10a0383355d","tid":47942,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"咪即係雞"},{"pid":"ece38e6a9437850404e5caa427fefd440e924b1f","tid":47942,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係要黎屌都介意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc0a3cf8265171422c0de5a65ad79b817d34970","tid":47942,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"女朋友唔係殺人放火以前做過咩真係咁重要咩"},{"pid":"ebae3bbcb79ebac0ea0d6ccc3b04d3199677a53d","tid":47942,"uid":66135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:12:54.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好放棄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩姿勢都識既女朋友好難再遇到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6a1f19e511b9330a1a78d2cd3fa22ee6a6edb1","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友唔係殺人放火以前做過咩真係咁重要咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你岩既 但怕太濫交我唔知 仲要係為名牌"},{"pid":"fe63a3d665c7a6447b70f3c686280a62781d57cf","tid":47942,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千祈唔好放棄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩姿勢都識既女朋友好難再遇到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc73a6817632c7f4c469b73e22ed43bb2d9c9a84","tid":47942,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"1.就算你諗佢唔同人出街既 你心裏都會有條刺 你一搵佢唔到 你就有排諗佢係咪去左開工<br />\n2.佢真係無同人出過街？燈紅酒綠大家飲到咁上下打個茄輪當食生菜啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有你話佢係想買名牌先走去返 咁訓一晚可以有個幾萬蚊既手袋 你訓唔訓？<br />\n<br />\n樓主自己諗清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我朋友都好似你咁一開頭會好似接受到 但一發生左啲信任危機 之後佢好就好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 了<br />\n(我朋友仲要一開始就知)<br />\n<br />\n利申:成日去夜總會<br />\n<br />\n樓主你睇完可能想講粗口屌我老母 但係我真係唔想又多一個受害者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街死港女 去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正臭雞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你女朋友係邊個場做？返工叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47b54cfba65886685d0ba82559343a90dd27900","tid":47942,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女朋友唔係殺人放火以前做過咩真係咁重要咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你岩既 但怕太濫交我唔知 仲要係為名牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為左名牌又真係太過份嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 養家都話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時覺得香港女仔真係俾小部分嘅人影衰曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae04d23f91055d4673f0e89c0972591e0a5981c7","tid":47942,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係要黎屌都介意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫佢食屎啦 唔介意個啲9成5-60歲呃妹妹仔先講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86d6f49a72739683b72edcf50fe7d5a8fc0d89a","tid":47942,"uid":67190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱戀期先知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續愛住先囉 感覺無可能話消失就消失<br />\n當條刺拔唔到 日子耐左你都會同佢分手<br />\n何況仲未穩定到談婚論嫁既階段<br />\n介唔介意講你地幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25 26 <br />\n但佢仲話好多男人都唔會介意 我以為係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n免費點解要介意，認真既點都會有d介意啦"},{"pid":"a7ef350a14c9a5af56f475da11eb0e7013466545","tid":47942,"uid":67190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金魚都接受到既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金魚會唔會都偷偷比啲唔識既叔叔扑？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇人既"},{"pid":"e3b22d6d3c1651b63b4b1530d67a8e1f43aeab47","tid":47942,"uid":67190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為物慾去做嘅飛硬<br />\n隨時一路同你拍拖一路繼續做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就應該無再做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉為叫你買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f355919ef2c3d6a624a325726be9b2716a2f2c8","tid":47942,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:26:57.000Z","msg":"而家仲邊有夜總會呀？<br />\n旺角果d?<br />\n即屌埋果種？"},{"pid":"506b6c5d93f05c7530decc85fd461beaa672cad4","tid":47942,"uid":67190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係有錢佬 只係對佢好好啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢放唔放得低d名牌？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會叫我搵錢買....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你滿足唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人點同一班人比"},{"pid":"7767f15a8f1ee4214b876af8943c5938dbf2c05f","tid":47942,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家仲邊有夜總會呀？<br />\n旺角果d?<br />\n即屌埋果種？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n私人會所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲好真係好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786c1e5aa82e8dfad06e536405f251a31b7c4895","tid":47942,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家仲邊有夜總會呀？<br />\n旺角果d?<br />\n即屌埋果種？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n私人會所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲女真係好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2f7205e8b06d7fa37801a09487b7774d2be29287","tid":47942,"uid":67190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會叫我搵錢買....</blockquote><br />\n即係咪又係雞，仲要話其他男人唔介意，你回頭就唔介意，但點睇佢都係無人要隻臭雞之後搵毒丁埋單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身邊有幾個朋友都同夜總會小姐結婚。。我都唔個係我太介意定點 結婚真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩都晒錢 咁多朋友同夜總會小姐結婚 個到識架？"},{"pid":"2c7e9e6174001bff4db6ea4402d9025215c92a8c","tid":47942,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家仲邊有夜總會呀？<br />\n旺角果d?<br />\n即屌埋果種？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n私人會所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲女真係好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n私人會所又唔同<br />\n真係有金魚的"},{"pid":"a104afc05b7b8ec4ae808c7ec16aa0d5c947c364","tid":47942,"uid":22291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係女友屋企開夜總會又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪江湖中人 係咪冇所謂"},{"pid":"6979d9388a3115014455648a95ecdb6d2ec9c0ec","tid":47942,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"一街都㩒兄弟啦老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd34f247679ca4ba8a7a2695cf58428421b1521","tid":47942,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"老納贈師主一句<br />\n四海之內皆襟兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi